title: Welcome To Ana’s Blog
text: This is Sox - he is one and a half years old and he is looking for this forever home. He has been vaccinated and neutered. However, he tested positive for Leukemia and can’t be around any other cats. He needs to be the only cat in the household. He loves to play, sleep on his back and follow his human around.
